room_title: Escape room "The Garage" by D.O.A. Room Escape in Chicago
room_address: 717 N. Iowa Ave. Villa Park, IL 60181
room_description: Travel back in time to the Saint Valentine's Day, 1929. It's memorable not for roses and candy hearts, but for the gruesome Massacre by Al Capone's gang. Now, he has a special job just for you. Meet him at the garage, and be sure to hold up your end of the bargain, or become the eighth victim tonight...
